        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>multiple dwellings [300005703], dwellings [300005425], residential structures [300257729], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hotels providing apartments, usually furnished, to long-term tenants and including some services not available to the general public. For similar housing but providing smaller accommodations for short- or long-term rental at very low rates, often with shared facilities, and fewer services, use "single room occupancy hotels."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hotel que proporciona apartamentos, generalmente amueblados, para inquilinos de largo plazo y que inlcluye algunos servicios no disponibles para público general. Para alojamientos similares pero que proporcionan instalaciones menores para alquilados de corto o largo plazo a muy bajas tarifas, frecuentemente con instalaciones compartidas y menos servicios, use "hotel de habitaciones individuales”.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hotels die meestal gemeubileerde appartementen bieden voor langdurige huur, met inbegrip van bepaalde diensten die niet algemeen beschikbaar zijn. Gebruik 'logementen (1)' voor soortgelijk onderdak maar met kleinere verblijven voor korte of lange huurperiodes, tegen zeer lage prijzen en met minder diensten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hotel, das gewöhnlich möblierte Apartments für Langzeitmieter zur Verfügung stellt und einige Dienstleistungen einschließt, die der breiten Öffentlichkeit nicht zur Verfügung stehen. Für eine ähnliche Unterkunft, die aber kleinere Wohnungen für kurz- oder längerfristige Vermietung zu sehr niedrigen Raten bereitstellt, oftmals gemeinsam genutze Einrichtungen hat und weniger Dienstleistungen, siehe "Single Room Occupancy Hotel".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>提供附家具及專屬住戶服務、可長期租賃之公寓的飯店。若是租金低廉、空間較小、通常需共用設備且提供之服務較少之短期或長期租賃的類似住所，則稱為「單身公寓飯店」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
